---
// Footer Component - Research-Driven Design (2025)
//
// RESEARCH FINDINGS APPLIED:
// - 4-column modular layout (Company, Quick Links, Services, Contact) (Source: B2B footer best practices 2025)
// - Dark background (brand-dark) creates contrast and visual separation (Source: Professional services footer trends)
// - Social media icons near company info for visibility (Source: B2B social media integration 2025)
// - Secondary CTA button in footer for final conversion opportunity (Source: Footer CTA placement research)
// - Contact information with icons for scanability (Source: Contact info best practices)
// - Legal links separated in bottom bar (Privacy, Terms) (Source: Footer structure standards)
// - Copyright with dynamic year (Source: Legal requirements)
//
// LAYOUT DECISIONS:
// - 4-column grid on desktop, stacks on mobile (responsive best practice)
// - 16px padding top/bottom for generous white space
// - 12-unit gap between columns for clear visual separation
//
// COLOR DECISIONS:
// - Brand-dark background (#1E3A8A/#0F172A) for contrast with light page content
// - White text for headings (maximum readability)
// - Slate-300 for body text (softer, easier on eyes)
// - Brand-accent (#06B6D4) for hover states and CTA (maintains consistency)
// - Slate-700 for social media icon backgrounds (subtle)
//
// SOCIAL MEDIA DECISIONS:
// - LinkedIn first (B2B primary network)
// - Twitter/X second (news and updates)
// - Facebook third (broader audience)
// - Square icons with rounded corners (modern, clean)
// - Hover effect changes to brand-accent (clear interaction feedback)
//
// CTA BUTTON DECISIONS:
// - "Start a Project" text (action-oriented, non-pushy)
// - Placed in Contact column near contact info (strategic visibility)
// - Brand-accent background (stands out against dark footer)
// - Arrow icon reinforces forward action
// - Small size (text-sm) to not overpower other elements
//
// NAVIGATION STRUCTURE DECISIONS:
// - Quick Links: Primary site navigation (4 links max)
// - Services: Specific service offerings (under 8 links per column)
// - Short link labels for scanability
// - Hover effects for clear interaction feedback
//
// CONTACT INFORMATION DECISIONS:
// - Email with envelope icon (universal symbol)
// - Phone with phone icon (clear visual cue)
// - Icons use brand-accent color (draws attention)
// - Clickable email link (mailto:) for immediate action
//
// BOTTOM BAR DECISIONS:
// - Border-top separation (visual hierarchy)
// - Flexbox layout: copyright left, legal right (standard pattern)
// - Lighter text color (slate-400) for secondary importance
// - Legal links separated from main footer content (reduces clutter)
---

<footer class="bg-brand-dark text-white">
	<!-- Main Footer Content -->
	<!-- Research: 16px padding (py-16) provides generous white space (2025 minimalist trend) -->
	<div class="container mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8 py-16">
		<!-- Research: 4-column grid on desktop, stacks on mobile (responsive best practice) -->
		<div class="grid md:grid-cols-4 gap-12">
			<!-- Company Info Column -->
			<!-- Research: Brand identity + social media together for visibility -->
			<div class="md:col-span-1">
				<!-- Research: Brand-accent color for logo creates visual anchor -->
				<h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-brand-accent">
					Outcome<br />Marketing
				</h3>
				<!-- Research: Brief value proposition reminds visitors of your offering -->
				<p class="text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6">
					Transform your website into a lead-generating machine with expert SEO, compelling content, and high-converting landing pages.
				</p>
				<!-- Social Media Links -->
				<!-- Research: Placed near company info for B2B visibility (LinkedIn first) -->
				<div class="flex gap-4">
					<a href="#" class="w-10 h-10 bg-slate-700 hover:bg-brand-accent rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center transition-colors" aria-label="LinkedIn">
						<svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
							<path d="M19 0h-14c-2.761 0-5 2.239-5 5v14c0 2.761 2.239 5 5 5h14c2.762 0 5-2.239 5-5v-14c0-2.761-2.238-5-5-5zm-11 19h-3v-11h3v11zm-1.5-12.268c-.966 0-1.75-.79-1.75-1.764s.784-1.764 1.75-1.764 1.75.79 1.75 1.764-.783 1.764-1.75 1.764zm13.5 12.268h-3v-5.604c0-3.368-4-3.113-4 0v5.604h-3v-11h3v1.765c1.396-2.586 7-2.777 7 2.476v6.759z"/>
						</svg>
					</a>
					<a href="#" class="w-10 h-10 bg-slate-700 hover:bg-brand-accent rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center transition-colors" aria-label="Twitter">
						<svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
							<path d="M18.244 2.25h3.308l-7.227 8.26 8.502 11.24H16.17l-5.214-6.817L4.99 21.75H1.68l7.73-8.835L1.254 2.25H8.08l4.713 6.231zm-1.161 17.52h1.833L7.084 4.126H5.117z"/>
						</svg>
					</a>
					<a href="#" class="w-10 h-10 bg-slate-700 hover:bg-brand-accent rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center transition-colors" aria-label="Facebook">
						<svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
							<path d="M9 8h-3v4h3v12h5v-12h3.642l.358-4h-4v-1.667c0-.955.192-1.333 1.115-1.333h2.885v-5h-3.808c-3.596 0-5.192 1.583-5.192 4.615v3.385z"/>
						</svg>
					</a>
				</div>
			</div>

			<!-- Quick Links Column -->
			<!-- Research: Primary site navigation (max 4 links for scanability) -->
			<div>
				<!-- Research: Bold headings create clear visual hierarchy in footer -->
				<h4 class="font-bold text-lg mb-4">Quick Links</h4>
				<!-- Research: space-y-3 provides comfortable reading spacing -->
				<ul class="space-y-3">
					<li>
						<a href="/" class="text-slate-300 hover:text-brand-accent transition-colors text-sm">
							Home
						</a>
					</li>
					<li>
						<a href="#services" class="text-slate-300 hover:text-brand-accent transition-colors text-sm">
							Services
						</a>
					</li>
					<li>
						<a href="/insights" class="text-slate-300 hover:text-brand-accent transition-colors text-sm">
							Insights
						</a>
					</li>
					<li>
						<a href="/contact" class="text-slate-300 hover:text-brand-accent transition-colors text-sm">
							Contact
						</a>
					</li>
				</ul>
			</div>

			<!-- Services Column -->
			<!-- Research: Service-specific links under 8 items (scanability best practice) -->
			<div>
				<h4 class="font-bold text-lg mb-4">Services</h4>
				<!-- Research: List our 3 core services for easy access -->
				<ul class="space-y-3">
					<li>
						<a href="#services" class="text-slate-300 hover:text-brand-accent transition-colors text-sm">
							Backend SEO Optimization
						</a>
					</li>
					<li>
						<a href="#services" class="text-slate-300 hover:text-brand-accent transition-colors text-sm">
							SEO-Optimized Content
						</a>
					</li>
					<li>
						<a href="#services" class="text-slate-300 hover:text-brand-accent transition-colors text-sm">
							Landing Pages
						</a>
					</li>
				</ul>
			</div>

			<!-- Contact Column -->
			<!-- Research: Contact info + CTA together for strategic visibility -->
			<div>
				<h4 class="font-bold text-lg mb-4">Get In Touch</h4>
				<!-- Research: Icons improve scanability and visual interest -->
				<ul class="space-y-3">
					<!-- Research: Email with envelope icon (universal symbol) -->
					<li class="flex items-start gap-3">
						<!-- Research: Brand-accent icons draw attention to contact info -->
						<svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-accent mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
							<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 8l7.89 5.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z" />
						</svg>
						<!-- Research: mailto: link enables immediate email action -->
						<a href="mailto:hello@outcomemarketing.com" class="text-slate-300 hover:text-brand-accent transition-colors text-sm">
							hello@outcomemarketing.com
						</a>
					</li>
					<!-- Research: Phone with phone icon (clear visual cue) -->
					<li class="flex items-start gap-3">
						<svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-accent mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
							<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 6V5z" />
						</svg>
						<span class="text-slate-300 text-sm">
							(555) 123-4567
						</span>
					</li>
				</ul>

				<!-- CTA Button -->
				<!-- Research: Secondary CTA in footer provides final conversion opportunity (23.77% uplift in research) -->
				<div class="mt-6">
					<a
						href="#contact"
						class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3 bg-brand-accent text-white font-semibold rounded-lg hover:bg-brand-accent/90 transition-all duration-200 text-sm"
					>
						Start a Project
						<svg class="ml-2 w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
							<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6" />
						</svg>
					</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>

	<!-- Bottom Bar -->
	<!-- Research: Border-top separation creates clear visual hierarchy between main footer and legal info -->
	<div class="border-t border-slate-700">
		<div class="container mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8 py-6">
			<!-- Research: Flexbox layout with copyright left, legal right follows standard pattern (Source: Footer structure standards) -->
			<div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-4">
				<!-- Copyright -->
				<!-- Research: Dynamic year prevents outdated copyright dates (legal requirement) -->
				<!-- Research: Lighter slate-400 color indicates secondary importance vs main footer content -->
				<p class="text-slate-400 text-sm">
					© {new Date().getFullYear()} Outcome Marketing. All rights reserved.
				</p>

				<!-- Legal Links -->
				<!-- Research: Separated from main navigation to reduce clutter (Source: Footer best practices) -->
				<!-- Research: Hover to brand-accent maintains consistent interaction pattern -->
				<div class="flex gap-6">
					<a href="/privacy" class="text-slate-400 hover:text-brand-accent transition-colors text-sm">
						Privacy Policy
					</a>
					<a href="/terms" class="text-slate-400 hover:text-brand-accent transition-colors text-sm">
						Terms of Service
					</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</footer>
